quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,“Ndithu tidampatsa mphamvu zokhalira pa dziko ndikumpatsa njira yopezera chilichonse
  18,85,“Choncho adatsata njira
  18,86,"“Mpaka pomwe adafika kumlowero kwa dzuwa (ku maiko a kuzambwe), adaliona (ngati) likulowa pa dziwe la matope ambiri. Ndipo pompo adapeza anthu; tidati: “E iwe Thul-Qarnain! Alange, kapena achitire zabwino.”"
  18,87,"“Adati: “Koma amene achita zosalungama timulanga; ndipo kenako adzabwezedwa kwa Mbuye wake; ndipo akamukhaulitsa ndi chilango choipa"
  18,88,"“Koma amene akhulupirire ndikuchita ntchito zabwino, apeza mphoto yabwino; ndipo timuuza zomwe zili zofewa m’zinthu zathu.”"
  18,89,“Kenako adatsata njira
  18,90,“Mpaka adafika ku mtulukiro kwa dzuwa (ku maiko akuvuma). Adalipeza (dzuwalo) likuwatulukira anthu omwe sitidawaikire chowatchinga ku ilo
  18,91,"“Momwemo, tidali kudziwa bwino nkhani zonse zomwe zidali ndi iye"
  18,92,“Kenako adatsata njira
  18,93,“Mpaka pomwe adafika pakatikati pa mapiri awiri adapeza pafupi ndi mapiriwo anthu omwe sikudali kwapafupi kumva chiyankhulo
  18,94,"“Adati: “E iwe Zul-Qarnain! Ndithu Yaajuju ndi Maajuju akuononga pa dziko. Kodi sikungatheke kuti tikupatse malipiro kuti uike pakati pathu ndi pakati pawo, chotchinga (mpanda)?”"
  18,95,"“(Iye) adati: “Zomwe Mbuye wanga wandipatsa ndi zabwino. Choncho ndithandizeni ndi mphamvu zanu (zonse pantchito imeneyi) ndiika chotchinga cholimba pakati panu ndi pakati pawo.”"
  18,96,"““Ndipatseni zidutswa za zitsulo.” Kufikira pamene adadzaza ndi zitsulozo mpata umene udalipo pakati pa mapiri awiriwo, adati: “Pemelerani (moto).” Mpaka (chitsulocho) chidafiira monga moto, adati: “Ndibweretsereni mtovu wosungunuka ndiuthire pamwamba pake (pa chitsulocho).”"
  18,97,"“Choncho (Yaajuju ndi Maajuju) sadathe kukwera pamwamba pake, ndiponso sadathe kuchiboola"